50|$|Whether {{a rental}} payment by a cash basis {{taxpayer}} for a lease year that extended eleven months beyond the <b>year</b> <b>of</b> <b>payment</b> is fully deductible in the <b>year</b> <b>of</b> <b>payment</b> as an ordinary and necessary business expense or must be deducted on a prorated basis as a capital expenditure.|$|E
