5000|$|The IBR Plan has {{different}} {{terms and conditions}} depending on when the student borrowed. If the borrower is a [...] "new borrower" [...] on or after July 1, 2014, then the borrower will have payments that are generally 10% of discretionary income and forgiveness is provided for after 20 <b>years</b> <b>of</b> qualifying <b>payment.</b> If a borrower {{is not a new}} borrower on or after July 1, 2014, then payments will generally be 15% of discretionary income and forgiveness is provided for after 25 <b>years</b> <b>of</b> qualifying repayment.|$|R
